OL,3,CNew cancer centre given the go-ahead
OL,5,FA new regional cancer centre for
OL,6,Fpatients across Sussex has been given
OL,7,Fthe go-ahead.
OL,9,FIt will cost #150 million to build and
OL,10,Fwill replace an 'old, leaky building'
OL,11,Fat the Royal Sussex County Hospital in
OL,12,FBrighton, which was due to be
OL,13,Fdemolished 10 years ago.
OL,15,FThe money, from the Government's new
OL,16,Fhospitals programme, will be invested
OL,17,Fin better facilities, state-of- the
OL,18,Fart equipment and research. The aim is
OL,19,Fto boost care and treatment for
OL,20,Fpatients
