OL,3,CNew cancer centre given the go-ahead
OL,5,FWork to demolish the old building that
OL,6,Fused to stand on this site began in
OL,7,FJanuary of last year.
OL,9,FThe NHS says 1 in 2 people will
OL,10,Fdevelop some form of cancer during
OL,11,Ftheir lifetime.
OL,13,FBill Shay, who has skin cancer has
OL,14,Fregular visits to the cancer unit at
OL,15,Fthe Royal Sussex County Hospital in
OL,16,FBrighton.
