OL,3,CNew cancer centre given the go-ahead
OL,5,FHe says he can't fault his care but,
OL,6,F"there are sometimes not enough chairs
OL,7,Fin the chemo with these big comfy
OL,8,Fchairs, the easy chairs to have the
OL,9,Finfusions."
OL,11,FThe roof in the current building is
OL,12,Fleaking which can damage equipment and
OL,13,Fsometimes delay care and treatment.
OL,15,FPreparation work for the new building
OL,16,Fis underway and planning permission
OL,17,Fhas just been granted for the new
OL,18,Fcancer centre, that is likely to open
OL,19,Fin 2029.
